  {
    "key": "f23d8716f8223cfdf78effc1571a4367bea2bafdd0ddd26651a37ee5abfd53a5",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_05.png[/img]A shadow crosses over you from behind. When you look back, %brawler% is standing there with a rather distant look in his eyes. He cracks his knuckles in one long staccato before asking if he can train up %noncom%. You ask why. The brawler looks down at you.%SPEECH_ON%Because he is weak.%SPEECH_OFF%Hmmm, good enough.",
